trans-unit.source: Provides a base implementation of a channel object that exposes a dictionary interface to its properties.
trans-unit.target: Oferece uma implementação base de um objeto de canal que expõe uma interface de dicionário a suas propriedades.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelObjectWithProperties> is the base class for <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelWithProperties> and <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelSinkWithProperties>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelObjectWithProperties> é a classe base para <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelWithProperties> e <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelSinkWithProperties>.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelWithProperties> and <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelSinkWithProperties> can be used as the base classes for channels and channel sinks that provide named properties.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelWithProperties> e <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelSinkWithProperties> podem ser usadas como classes base para canais e Coletores de canal que fornecem propriedades com nome.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelObjectWithProperties> handles the complex task of asking a channel object for its properties.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelObjectWithProperties> lida com a tarefa complexa de solicitar a um objeto do canal para suas propriedades.

trans-unit.source: This class makes a link demand and an inheritance demand at the class level.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe faz uma demanda de link e uma demanda de herança no nível de classe.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Security.SecurityException> is thrown when either the immediate caller or the derived class does not have infrastructure permission.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Security.SecurityException> é gerada quando o chamador imediato ou classe derivada não tem permissão de infraestrutura.

trans-unit.source: For details about security demands, see [Link Demands](~/docs/framework/misc/link-demands.md) and [Inheritance Demands](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/28b9adbb-8f08-4f10-b856-dbf59eb932d9).
trans-unit.target: Para obter detalhes sobre as exigências de segurança, consulte [demandas de Link](~/docs/framework/misc/link-demands.md) e [demandas de herança](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/28b9adbb-8f08-4f10-b856-dbf59eb932d9).

trans-unit.source: For operating with infrastructure code.
trans-unit.target: para a operação com código de infraestrutura.
